        "description": "Replays a firmware escalation window: 0 (quiescent) \u2192 1 (brief) \u2192 3 (sustained) \u2192 6 (severe, firmware ceiling). Each step exercises a different threshold band. Final tick must classify as MOTION_SEVERE (ordinal 3).",
        "vectors": [
